{"tid":1565710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一位香港文化界朋友的意見","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T14:14:53.000Z","uid":109847,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f11789bf08b87cbd4e45e2ea9baff967a2fd4162","tid":1565710,"uid":109847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》唔押韻同有啲唔啱音，我嘗試改良：<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">怒滿城 滴血汗</span></strong><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如水勇共謀</span></strong> 吶喊聲響透<br />\n盼自由 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今天釋</span>放</strong><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盲眼</span></strong> 這恐懼 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">恨似仇</span> </strong><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還眼</span></strong> 為信念 從沒 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">怯懦</span></strong><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人身</span></strong> 血在流 但邁進聲響透<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戴著頭盔豬嘴抵抗</span></strong><br />\n在晚星墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來號角聲<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗極權</span></strong> 來齊集這裡 來 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同共進退</span></strong><br />\n勇氣 智慧 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到處激盪</span></strong><br />\n黎明來到 要光復 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">耀我城</span></strong><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求民主與自由 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歷劫增添堅壯</span></strong><br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">915 維園見<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7d2a799e8bcd88a767e080dbd2c39dae6e85087","tid":1565710,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\